data.name: categoryId
data.description: Filter included points of interest (Eg. railway stations, car parks, ATMs) returned by category id

data.name: includePois
data.description: true or false

data.name: includeReviews
data.description: true or false

data.name: key
data.description: API key (required)

data.name: query
data.description: Unique ID of the listing to return (required)

data.name: datatype
data.description: The type of metadata (required)

data.name: key
data.description: API key (required)

data.name: boundingBox
data.description: Bounding box to serve as a hint to disambiguate the "what" within the query, E.g. "richmond" exists in several states, so if the bounding box is in Victoria, then it is interpreted as "Richmond Vic". However, if the query does not contain a "where" part, the centre of the boundingBox is used as the search location.

data.name: location
data.description: Your CURRENT location as latitude,longitude, e.g. -37.7833,144.9667. It serves only as a hint to disambiguate the "what" within the query if the boundingBox is not provided. E.g. "richmond" exists in several states. So if your current location is in Victoria, then it is interpreted as "Richmond Vic". Note that unlike the boundingBox, this is never used to derive the search location.

data.name: mappable
data.description: A value of true means that only listings with geocode granularity of PROPERTY or INTERSECTION will be returned. This means that these listings can be reliably used by mapping or geographical applications.

data.name: query
data.description: Combinations of "what" or "where", either of which are optional, and can optionally be separated by a join word. (required)

data.name: sortBy
data.description: Does not support DISTANCE or DISTANCE_ALL_PAGES. (You will get a misleading error message if you try.)

data.name: content
data.description: Specific content to which the event applies (required

data.name: id
data.description: reportingId of listing associated with event (required)

data.name: key
data.description: API key (required)

data.name: userAgent
data.description: User agent of user accessing your application

data.name: userIp
data.description: IP address of user accessing your application (required)

data.name: userSessionId
data.description: Session id of user accessing your application

data.name: aboutid
data.description: aboutId is one of the Sensis ID attributes returned from getByListingId endpoint.

data.name: key
data.description: API key (required)

data.name: limit
data.description: Limit is used for pagination. The number of reviews after their offset to return. Limit is the same as page size. Default: 10

data.name: namespace
data.description: Namespace is used as a filter. Only reviews for this given namespace will be returned. e.g. http://www.yelp.com.au.

data.name: offset
data.description: Offset is used for pagination. The zero based number of the review to start from. The reviews that start from this offset will be returned. Default: 0

data.name: sortOrder
data.description: ASC - sort the reviews ascending or smallest to largest.  DESC - sort the reviews descending or largest to smallest. DESC.

data.name: sortType
data.description: DATE - the date reviews are submitted. RATING - the number of ratings for each of the review. Default: DATE.

data.name: boundingBox
data.description: Filter listings returned to those within a bounding box.

data.name: categoryId
data.description: Filter listings returned by category id

data.name: content
data.description: Filter listings returned to only those with certain types of content.

data.name: includePois
data.description: A value of true will mean the response will include any relevant points of interest (Eg. railway stations, car parks, ATMs).

data.name: key
data.description: Use your Test API Key. Required field.

data.name: location
data.description: Location to search in. Required unless query is given.

data.name: locationTiers
data.description: Filter listings returned to those within a number of location tiers of the location.

data.name: page
data.description: Page number to return.

data.name: postcode
data.description: Filter listings returned by postcode

data.name: productKeyword
data.description: Filter listings returned to only those containing certain product keywords.

data.name: query
data.description: What to search for. Required unless location is given.

data.name: radius
data.description: Filter listings returned to those within the radius distance of the location.

data.name: rows
data.description: Number of listings to return per page.

data.name: sensitiveCategories
data.description: Filtering potentially unsafe content.

data.name: sortBy
data.description: Listing sort order.

data.name: state
data.description: Filter listings returned to those within the given state. Repeat the parameter to include multiple states in the filter.

data.name: suburb
data.description: Filter listings returned to those within the given suburb. Repeat the parameter to include multiple suburbs in the filter.
